QuestData.Title: Lawn of the Dead
QuestData.Description: IT'S STILLWATER! HE'S ALMOST HERE! It's going to take everything that we've got to beat him! Let's do this!
QuestData.RewardText: I can't believe we defeated him, $n! That was the toughest fight yet, but there are still hundreds of crazed zombies roaming around Hillsbrad. We'll need to stay alert.
